എൻ്റെ കൂടെ  ബീസ്റ്റ് ഗെയിംസിൽ പങ്കാളികളായതിന് മണി ലയണിന് നന്ദി. ബീസ്റ്റ് ഗെയിംസ് നടക്കുമ്പോൾ $4,000,000 ലധികം നേടാനായി ഇപ്പോൾ തന്നെ മണിലയൺ ബീസ്റ്റ് ഗെയിംസ് ഗിവ്എവേയിൽ പ്രവേശിക്കൂ ഈ ലിങ്കിലൂടെ പ്രവേശിയ്കൂ https://www.moneylion.com/beastgames!. നിരവധി തവണ രജിസ്റ്റർ ചെയ്ത് ബീസ്റ്റ് ബോണസ് നേടിക്കൊണ്ട്  നിങ്ങളുടെ വിജയ സാധ്യത വർധിപ്പിക്കാനായി ഇപ്പോൾ തന്നെ മണിലയൺ ആപ്പ് ഡൌൺലോഡ് ചെയ്യൂ.

സമയത്തിരക്ക് മൂലവും ചില മത്സരാർത്ഥികൾക്ക് പങ്കെടുക്കാൻ സാധിക്കാത്തത് മൂലവും ഈ വീഡിയോയിൽ നിന്നും എലിമിനേറ്റായ 50 ആളുകളെ ബീസ്റ്റ് ഗെയിംസ് എപ്പിസോഡ് ഒന്നിൽ പങ്കെടുക്കാനായി ഞങ്ങൾ ക്രമരഹിതമായി തിരഞ്ഞെടുക്കപ്പെട്ടിരുന്നു.    

എല്ലാ പുറത്താകലുകൾക്കും തീരുമാനങ്ങൾക്കും മുന്നേ ഫൂട്ടേജുകൾ റിവ്യൂ ചെയ്തിട്ടുണ്ട്. മത്സരാർത്ഥികളുടെ ചെയ്തികളും ഇത് ബാധകമാണ്.    

തങ്ങളുടെ മനോഹരമായ സ്റ്റേഡിയത്തിലേക്ക് ഞങ്ങളെ സ്വീകരിച്ച ലാസ് വേഗാസ് റൈഡേഴ്സിനും അല്ലിജിയന്‍റ്  സ്റ്റേഡിയത്തിനും നന്ദി.

Episode 4271: Shaadi Ki Umr
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide is concerned about Sonu’s friendship with Tapu, fearing it might blossom into love. How will he come to terms with the fact that his daughter is now a grown up?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
In this video, join me as I transform our home into a cozy Christmas wonderland! This year, I’m mixing traditional holiday charm with creative DIY touches to make our decorations truly special. From twinkling fairy lights and garlands to homemade ornaments and festive centerpieces, you’ll find plenty of inspiration for your own holiday decor. In this video, I tried making a 2D Christmas tree on the wall and decorating it with ornaments.

#christmashomedecor #holidaydecorations #steffivlogs

From crafting unique tree ornaments to styling a festive mantelpiece, these ideas are perfect for families who love to get creative and embrace the holiday spirit. I hope this week’s vlog inspires you to deck your halls and enjoy a joyful holiday season. Don’t forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more festive fun. See you soon with another cheerful video!

snippet.description:
Get Ready For The Biggest Blockbuster Flashing Worldwide 🔥! The Icon Star 'Allu Arjun' & the Dancing Queen 'Sreeleela' Is Coming to Rock The Floor!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings. The film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Navin Nooli respectively.

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

BJP MLC C.T. Ravi Arrested; An FIR has been filed against BJP MLC C.T. Ravi at the Hirebagawadi Police Station in Belagavi Taluk. The FIR was registered based on a complaint filed by Secretary Lakshmi Hebbalkar. The case has been registered under BNS Sections 75 and 79.

ಸಿ.ಟಿ. ರವಿ ಬಂಧನ; ಬಿಜೆಪಿ ಎಂಎಲ್‌ಸಿ ಸಿ.ಟಿ. ರವಿ ವಿರುದ್ಧ FIR ದಾಖಲು,ಬೆಳಗಾವಿ ತಾಲೂಕಿನ  ಹಿರೇಬಾಗೇವಾಡಿ ಠಾಣೆಯಲ್ಲಿ FIR, ಸಚಿವೆ ಲಕ್ಷ್ಮಿ ಹೆಬ್ಬಾಳ್ಕರ್‌ ನೀಡಿದ ದೂರಿನ ಮೇರೆಗೆ FIR, BNS ಕಲಂ 75, 79 ಅಡಿ ಎಫ್‌ಐಆರ್ ದಾಖಲು

snippet.title: PM Modi In Jaipur : Rajasthan को क्या-क्या दे गए PM Modi | देखिए लिस्ट | ERCP | CM Bhajan Lal Sharma
snippet.description:
#ERCP_National_Project #CMBhajanLalSharma #narendramodi 

PM Modi In Jaipur : Rajasthan को क्या-क्या दे गए PM Modi | देखिए पूरी लिस्ट | ERCP | CM Bhajan Lal | PM Modi Live | PM Modi Jaipur | PM Modi Live Today | PM Modi Speech Today | PM Modi Jaipur Live | PM Modi Jaipur | PM Modi Jaipur Live | PM Modi Jaipur Visit | PM Modi Jaipur Dadiya | PM Modi Jaipur Dora | Modi Live | Modi Live Today | Modi In Jaipur | ERCP Project In Rajasthan | ERCP Rajasthan | PKC ERCP Link Project | CM Bhajanlal Live Today | CM Bhajan Lal Sharma | CM Bhajanlal Live | Bhajan Lal Sharma Live | Breaking News | Rajasthan News | Rajasthan Politics | BJP | Congress | PM Modi On Congress

राजस्थान की भजनलाल सरकार एक साल का जश्न मना रही है.. इस जश्न में उस वक्त चार चांद लग गए.. जब प्रधानमंत्री नरेन्द्र मोदी दिल्ली से चलकर राजधानी जयपुर पहुंचे और प्रदेश को कई सौगात दे गए। दादिया में हुई जनसभा में पीएम मोदी ने पानी, बिजली, सड़क और रेलवे के साथ-साथ कुल 24 प्रोजेक्ट्स का लोकार्पण और शिलान्यास किया। पीएम मोदी ने लंबे समय से अटके पीकेसी-ईआरसीपी के पहले फेज का शिलान्यास किया। इस परियोजना के तहत 11 नदियों को जोड़ा गया, जिसके बाद अब कई जिलों को सिंचाई के लिए पानी के संकट का सामना नहीं करना पड़ेगा. इस दौरान पीएम मोदी ने कांग्रेस पर भी जमकर निशाना साधा। उन्होंने कहा कि कांग्रेस ने राजनीति करने के लिए पानी जैसी मूलभूत आवश्यकताओं को भी रोक दिया। कांग्रेस समाधान की बजाय राज्यों के बीच जल विवाद को बढ़ावा देती रही।

Bhajan Lal government of Rajasthan is celebrating its first anniversary. This celebration became even more special when Prime Minister Narendra Modi reached the capital Jaipur from Delhi and gave many gifts to the state. In the public meeting held in Dadiya, PM Modi inaugurated and laid the foundation stone of a total of 24 projects including water, electricity, road and railway. PM Modi laid the foundation stone of the first phase of the long-pending PKC-ERCP. Under this project, 11 rivers were connected, after which many districts will no longer have to face the problem of water for irrigation. During this, PM Modi also targeted Congress fiercely. He said that Congress stopped even the basic necessities like water for doing politics. Congress kept promoting water disputes between states instead of finding solutions.

hi.title: PM Modi In Jaipur : Rajasthan को क्या-क्या दे गए PM Modi | देखिए लिस्ट | ERCP | CM Bhajan Lal Sharma
hi.description:
#ERCP_National_Project #CMBhajanLalSharma #narendramodi 

PM Modi In Jaipur : Rajasthan को क्या-क्या दे गए PM Modi | देखिए पूरी लिस्ट | ERCP | CM Bhajan Lal | PM Modi Live | PM Modi Jaipur | PM Modi Live Today | PM Modi Speech Today | PM Modi Jaipur Live | PM Modi Jaipur | PM Modi Jaipur Live | PM Modi Jaipur Visit | PM Modi Jaipur Dadiya | PM Modi Jaipur Dora | Modi Live | Modi Live Today | Modi In Jaipur | ERCP Project In Rajasthan | ERCP Rajasthan | PKC ERCP Link Project | CM Bhajanlal Live Today | CM Bhajan Lal Sharma | CM Bhajanlal Live | Bhajan Lal Sharma Live | Breaking News | Rajasthan News | Rajasthan Politics | BJP | Congress | PM Modi On Congress

राजस्थान की भजनलाल सरकार एक साल का जश्न मना रही है.. इस जश्न में उस वक्त चार चांद लग गए.. जब प्रधानमंत्री नरेन्द्र मोदी दिल्ली से चलकर राजधानी जयपुर पहुंचे और प्रदेश को कई सौगात दे गए। दादिया में हुई जनसभा में पीएम मोदी ने पानी, बिजली, सड़क और रेलवे के साथ-साथ कुल 24 प्रोजेक्ट्स का लोकार्पण और शिलान्यास किया। पीएम मोदी ने लंबे समय से अटके पीकेसी-ईआरसीपी के पहले फेज का शिलान्यास किया। इस परियोजना के तहत 11 नदियों को जोड़ा गया, जिसके बाद अब कई जिलों को सिंचाई के लिए पानी के संकट का सामना नहीं करना पड़ेगा. इस दौरान पीएम मोदी ने कांग्रेस पर भी जमकर निशाना साधा। उन्होंने कहा कि कांग्रेस ने राजनीति करने के लिए पानी जैसी मूलभूत आवश्यकताओं को भी रोक दिया। कांग्रेस समाधान की बजाय राज्यों के बीच जल विवाद को बढ़ावा देती रही।

Bhajan Lal government of Rajasthan is celebrating its first anniversary. This celebration became even more special when Prime Minister Narendra Modi reached the capital Jaipur from Delhi and gave many gifts to the state. In the public meeting held in Dadiya, PM Modi inaugurated and laid the foundation stone of a total of 24 projects including water, electricity, road and railway. PM Modi laid the foundation stone of the first phase of the long-pending PKC-ERCP. Under this project, 11 rivers were connected, after which many districts will no longer have to face the problem of water for irrigation. During this, PM Modi also targeted Congress fiercely. He said that Congress stopped even the basic necessities like water for doing politics. Congress kept promoting water disputes between states instead of finding solutions.

snippet.description:
Two branches. One tree.
 
Jackie Chan, Ben Wang, and Ralph Macchio star in Karate Kid: Legends - exclusively in movie theatres May 30. #KarateKidMovie

Learn more: https://www.karatekid.movie
 
Subscribe to Sony Pictures for exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Follow Us On Social:
https://www.facebook.com/TheKarateKid/
https://twitter.com/karatekidmovie
https://www.instagram.com/karatekidmovie/
https://www.tiktok.com/@karatekidmovie

In Karate Kid: Legends, after a family tragedy, kung fu prodigy Li Fong (Ben Wang) is uprooted from his home in Beijing and forced to move to New York City with his mother. Li struggles to let go of his past as he tries to fit in with his new classmates, and although he doesn't want to fight, trouble seems to find him everywhere. When a new friend needs his help, Li enters a karate competition – but his skills alone aren't enough. Li's kung fu teacher Mr. Han (Jackie Chan) enlists original Karate Kid Daniel LaRusso (Ralph Macchio) for help, and Li learns a new way to fight, merging their two styles into one for the ultimate martial arts showdown.

Directed by: Jonathan Entwistle   
 
Written by: Rob Lieber    

Produced by: Karen Rosenfelt
          
Executive Producers:
Jenny Hinkey
Ralph Macchio

Cast:
Jackie Chan and Ralph Macchio
Ben Wang
Joshua Jackson
Sadie Stanley
Ming-Na Wen

snippet.description:

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

snippet.title: चम्मच भर दलिया सर्दी में ऐसे खालो घुटना-कमर,जोड़ों का दर्द कभी नहीं होगा calcium भरपूर मिलेगा |DALIYA
snippet.description:
#winterrecipebyeatyammiecious 
#energyboost #daliyarecipe 

चम्मच भर दलिया सर्दी में ऐसे खालो घुटना-कमर, जोड़ों का दर्द कभी नहीं होगा calcium भरपूर मिलेगा |Dalia

Daliya ki khir aur Daliya ke Labh se Sal mein aap kabhi bhi Banakar kha sakte hain lekin Is Tarah ka Daliya jismein ki Gond bhi hai yah aap sirf sardiyon Mein Hi kha sakte hain yah aapki sehat ke liye bahut jyada Achcha Rahega to is bar aap apne diet Mein yah Daliya Gond ke sath banaa Karke Jarur se add Karen

If you want to stay Healthy then never change your lifestyle you just have to include this healthy recipes in your diet.......

Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*INGREDIENTS required :-

1/3cup - Broken Wheat
1/4cup - Edible Gum
3/4cup - Dry Coconut
3 cup - Milk
1/4cup - Dates 
1/4cup - Jaggery Powder
8-10 - Almonds
8-10 - Cashews
1-2tbs - Raisins
1ts - Dry Ginger Powder
1 pinch - Nutmeg
1/2ts - White Pepper Powder
1/2ts - Green Cardamom Powder
3-4tbs - Clarified Butter

 

            Don't forget to follow these steps:)

● LIKE  ● SHARE ● SUBSCRIBE

snippet.title: Lipika ने Soumya को किया Expose | Mangal Lakshmi | मंगल लक्ष्मी | Sneak Peek
snippet.description:
📲 Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

Lipika ने Soumya को किया Expose | Mangal Lakshmi | मंगल लक्ष्मी | Sneak Peek
When Sowmya arrives to Lipika's wedding, Vrinda and other family members are visibly offended, igniting controversy. Further, Adit harshly reprimands Sowmya. How will Sowmya respond to this unexpected confrontation?
-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

snippet.description:
Today I'm going to share you the super healthy dates walnut cake without egg.This eggless date walnut cake is a wholesome treat, naturally sweetened with dates and packed with the goodness of crunchy walnuts. It’s a healthier twist on traditional cakes, made without eggs or the need for an oven. The cake is steamed or cooked on a stovetop, resulting in a soft and tender texture that feels indulgent yet light. Every bite combines the natural caramel-like sweetness of dates with the earthy richness of walnuts, making it a perfect guilt-free dessert. Simple, nourishing, and satisfying, it’s a delightful choice for health-conscious indulgence.Do try this healthy cake at home and leave your valuable feedback in comment section🤗.If you like this video please do like share & subscribe.

snippet.title: 🔴THANK YOU R ASHWIN🙌: KYA 11 MEIN JAGAH NAHI MILNE KI VAJAH SE LI RETIREMENT?
snippet.description:
BREAKING: R Ashwin has retired from international cricket with immediate effect, announcing his decision at the end of the third Test of the Border-Gavaskar Trophy series in Brisbane. Ashwin ends his Test career as India's second-highest wicket-taker in the format, with 537 wickets at an average of 24 in 106 Tests, only behind Anil Kumble, who finished with 619 wickets from 132 Tests. He played only one of the first three Tests of the ongoing series in Australia, taking 1 for 53 in the day-night fixture in Adelaide. In the previous series, the 3-0 defeat at home to New Zealand, Ashwin had picked up only nine wickets at an average of 41.22.

localized.title: 🔴THANK YOU R ASHWIN🙌: KYA 11 MEIN JAGAH NAHI MILNE KI VAJAH SE LI RETIREMENT?
localized.description:
BREAKING: R Ashwin has retired from international cricket with immediate effect, announcing his decision at the end of the third Test of the Border-Gavaskar Trophy series in Brisbane. Ashwin ends his Test career as India's second-highest wicket-taker in the format, with 537 wickets at an average of 24 in 106 Tests, only behind Anil Kumble, who finished with 619 wickets from 132 Tests. He played only one of the first three Tests of the ongoing series in Australia, taking 1 for 53 in the day-night fixture in Adelaide. In the previous series, the 3-0 defeat at home to New Zealand, Ashwin had picked up only nine wickets at an average of 41.22.

Episode 4270: Sonu Ki Chinta
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide is worried about Sonu’s future as he doesn’t trust Tapu and wants to find her a suitable groom as soon as possible. How will he cope with the stress of raising a growing daughter?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4270 | 17 Dec 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: सर्दी में सस्ता गुड़ - चना ऐसे खालो जिंदगी में कभी खुन की कमी नहीं होगी तंदूरस्ती भरपूर मिलेगी |Halwa
snippet.description:
#winterrecipebyeatyammiecious 
#energyboost #halwa 
सर्दी में सस्ता गुड़ - चना ऐसे खालो जिंदगी में कभी खुन की कमी नहीं होगी तंदूरस्ती भरपूर मिलेगी |Halwa

Agar aap gud aur chane ka halvai apni diet Mein Shamil Karenge to aapko kabhi bhi iron ki Kami Nahin Hogi Jiski vajah se Sharir mein Khoon Ki Kami bhi nahin Hogi Sath Mein Gud aur chana khane ka bahut jyada fayda hota hai Kyunki ismein protein aur iron donon ke hi Matra barabar se Pai Jaati Hai yah Hamare Sharir mein kisi bhi Tarah Ke nutritions ki Kami Nahin hone deta
So you have to try this recipe for your family health
Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*INGREDIENTS required :-

150g - Roasted Chana
200g - Jaggery
1 cup - Lotus Seeds
1/4cup - Almonds
2tbs - Poppy Seeds
1/2ts - White Pepper Powder
1/2ts - Dry Ginger Powder
1/2ts -/Green Cardamom Powder
4-5tbs - Clarified Butter

 

            Don't forget to follow these steps:)

Daya receives excellent news, while Jethalal leaves to attend a lecture. Khushi is about to meet a highly significant visitor to Gokuldham society. When Taarak shows in, Bhide is in the kitchen making tea and forgets he has set the tea pot on the heat.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1666
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG
